==Sleep==
[[File:Church of St Eustace Organ and Pulpit, Paris, France - Diliff.jpg|thumb|right|Interior of Saint-Eustache]]
Some of the most opulent hotels in the world are either in or very close to the 1st arrondissement, and there's some choice in the mid-range. Budget travellers, on the other hand, are probably better off in other, less central parts of town.

During fashion weeks, hotels, especially the 1st, are occupied by trade professionals and visitors, as well as brand showrooms. Finding a room can be a challenge and the rates go sky-high. Consult [https://fhcm.paris/en/paris-fashion-week-en/ Paris Fashion Week]{{Dead link|date=March 2023 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }} for fashion week dates and avoid them if you do not want to clash with it.

