===Mid-range=== * {{sleep | name=Hôtel Ermitage | alt= | url= | email= | address=42 bis, rue de l'Ermitage | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content=A small but intimate hotel that showcases some great views from its rooms. }}
===Splurge=== * {{sleep | name=Mama Shelter | alt= | url=http://www.mamashelter.com/ | email= | address=109, rue de Bagnolet | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | fax= | hours= |checkin= | checkout= | price= | content=A designer hotel with very comfortable rooms and Wi-Fi in all rooms.}}
==Stay safe== The 20th arrondissement has changed a lot since the early 2000s. While some areas remain underprivileged and not always very welcoming, most parts of the 20th are quiet, socially mixed neighbourhoods with many families.<!-- It's no risky to go to the flea market, the most likely is getting contributing to lung disease however. -->
General large city appropriate safety precautions are advised, especially if visiting late in the night.
