ng, but there is also a boulangerie and a bar down the street.}} * {{sleep | name=Hotel Secret de Paris | alt= | url=http://www.hotel-design-secret-de-paris.com/en/ | email=hotel@hotelsecretdeparis.com | address=2 rue de Parme | lat=48.88134 | long=2.32836 | directions= | phone=+33 1 53 16 33 33 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2015-09-03 | content=Boutique hotel of 29 rooms. }} * {{sleep | name=Hotel La Tour d'Auvergne | alt=Hotel Montmartre | url= | email= | address=10, rue de la Tour d'Auvergne | lat= | long= | directions=Metro Anvers, Poissonnière, Cadet | phone=+33 1 48 78 61 60 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content=On a street full of surprises. A few steps away from Montmartre, rue des Martyrs, Opéra, and avenue Trudaine. }} * {{sleep | name=Paris Hotel | url= | email= | address=23, rue Henri Monnier | lat= | long= | directions=Metro Pigalle or Saint Georges, both 400 m away | phone=+33 1 42 85 43 43 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price=Double room with a shower €85 | checkin= | checkout= | content=3 star near Pigalle. The rooms are of decent quality and the views of the street are charming and typically Parisian (lots of balconies and shutters at the front, and a pleasant garden view at the back.) There's free Wi-Fi in the rooms and a nice breakfast room. The street can get a little noisy at night, but that's typical of the area and probably not enough to keep you awake but you should be aware in case you happen to be a light sleeper. There is a Renault parking garage round the corner which charged €52 for 72 hours.}} * {{sleep | name=Quality Hotel Axel | alt=Charm Hotel | url=http://www.hotel-paris-axel.com/ | email=axelopera@my-paris-hotel.com | address=15, rue Montyon | lat= | long= | directions= | phone =+33 1 45 72 66 66 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | checkin= | checkout= | content=}} * {{sleep | name=Hôtel Saint Petersbourg Opéra | alt= | url=https://www.hotelsaintpetersbourg.com | email=info@hotelpeters.com | address=35 rue Caumartin | lat=48.87167 | long=2.32814 | directions=RER A - Auber / Paris Metro : Line 3 and 9 : Havre-Caumartin. Line 3, 7, and 8 : Opéra. Line 8, 12, and 14 - La Madeleine | phone=+33 1 42 66 60 38 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2018-03-08 | content=Founded in 1860, this elegant historic hotel was upgraded in 2016 to become a four-star hotel after a refit of some of its most important sections. }}
