 | phone= | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2025-10-22 | content=The Hilton is part of the CNIT convention centre. }} *{{sleep | name=Hotel Pullman Paris La Défense | alt= | url= | email= | address=11, av de l'Arche | lat=48.89499 | long=2.23898 | directions=North of CNIT and Grande Arche, accessible via a system of concrete walkways | phone=+33 1 47 17 50 00 | tollfree= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | lastedit=2025-10-22 | content=Renovated in 2013 as a part of Accor's initiative to refurbish all five Pullmans in Paris. Less expensive rooms retain much of the 1990s-style furniture, while the more expensive ones conform better to the current Pullman corporate standards. }} *{{sleep | name=Renaissance Paris Hotel La Défense | alt= | url=https://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/parld-renaissance-paris-la-defense-hotel/ | email= | address=60 Jardin de Valmy | lat=48.89265 | long=2.23287 | directions=Behind (west of) the Grande Arche | phone=+33 1 41 97 50 50 | tollfree= | fax= | checkin= | checkout= | price= | content= }} * {{sleep | name=Sofitel La Défense | alt= | url=https://all.accor.com/hotel/0912/index.en.shtml | email=H0912@sofitel.com | address=33,voie des Sculpteurs, 92800 Puteaux | lat=48.888133 | long=2.247219 | directions=The Sofitel is slightly hidden in a relatively low-rise mixed use building on the Esplanade. The only approach for motor vehicles is via the underground car park. It is best reached on foot from ''Esplanade de la Défense'' metro station. | phone=+33 1-47764443 | tollfree= | fax=+33 1-47767210 | checkin= | checkout= | price=€210 | content=There is nothing truly exceptional about the Sofitel La Défense, and the views out of the windows are downright unspectacular compared to other La Défense hotels, but this hotel garners good reviews by providing solid standards and reliable service for a fraction of the prices of downtown Sofitels. The hotel was renovated after 2010, with all but the cheapest ''Classic'' rooms getting new furnishings and bathrooms (with showers rather than bathtubs, a Paris rarity). }}
=== Courbevoie === The area around '''Place Charras''', in Courbevoie is a short bus ride or a 15-minute walk away from the metro. ==== Budget ==== * {{sleep | name=Adagio Access La Défense - Leonard da Vinci | alt= | url= | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | price= | checkin= | checkout=| content=Accor's no frills aparthotel.}} * {{sleep | name=Adagio Access La Défense Place Charras | alt=Citéa La Défense Place Charras | url=http://www.citea.com/apparthotels/paris-la-defense/citea-la-defense-place-charras- | email= | address=1, rue de Bitche | lat= | long= | directions=| phone=+33 1 56 37 72 00 | tollfree= | fax= | hours= | price= | checkin= | checkout= | content=It hosts foreign students from the Alliance Française in Paris.}} * {{sleep | name=ibis La Défense Courbevoie | alt= | url= | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | price= | checkin= | checkout=| content=}} ==== Mid-range ==== * {{sleep | name=Adagio La Défense Parc| alt= | url= | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | price= | checkin= | checkout=| content=Close to Adagio Access Leonard Da Vinci, an aparthotel of higher standard.}} * {{sleep | name=Adagio La Défense Kleber| alt= | url= | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions= | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | price= | checkin= | checkout=| content=A more upmarket neighbour of Adagio Access Place Charras}} * {{sleep | name=Kyriad Paris Ouest - La Défense Courbevoie | alt= | url= | email= | address= | lat= | long= | directions='''Northwards''' from Esplanade, close to the river. Not to be confused with the other Kyriad in Puteaux, which is also close to the river and a similar distance away from Esplanade, but in the opposite direction. | phone= | tollfree= | fax= | price= | checkin= | checkout=| content=}} *{{sleep | name=Hotel Mercure Paris La Défense 5 | alt= | url=https://all.accor.com/hotel/1546/index.en.shtml | email= | address=18-